These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, polish, british, indonesian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, rowing, rugby, tennis
1. the british is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's sport is rowing##2
2. the indonesian is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
3. the person who's sport is rugby is not to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##8
4. the person who's sport is rowing is not the british##6
5. the british is somewhere to the right of the argentine##5
6. the argentine is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Nationality   | indonesian  | argentine | british | polish  |
| Sport   | biathlon | rugby   | tennis  | rowing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
4 different games are played: bridge, backgammon, monopoly, scrabble
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, journalist, nurse, project-manager
1. the project-manager is not to the left of the project-manager##8
2. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the right of the person playing scrabble##5
3. the person playing bridge is the journalist##1
4. the person playing scrabble is between the person playing bridge and the person playing backgammon##2
5. the person playing backgammon is somewhere between the person playing monopoly and the designer##7
6. the nurse is somewhere to the left of the person playing backgammon##5
7. the designer is not to the left of the designer##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Game   | monopoly | backgammon          | scrabble | bridge     |
| Job    | nurse      | project-manager | designer | journalist |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, parkour, weightlifting, badminton
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, family, superhero
1. the person watching adventure movies is not to the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##8
2. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
4. the person who's sport is parkour is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere to the left of the person watching superhero movies##5
7. the person who's sport is badminton is the person watching family movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Sport           | handball | parkour | weightlifting     | badminton |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | superhero   | adventure | family    |

