.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
City: marseilles, paris, san-francisco, rome
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, handball, rugby
1. the person traveling to rome is somewhere between the person traveling to marseilles and the person traveling to paris##7
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is handball##5
3. the person traveling to rome is somewhere between the person traveling to san-francisco and the person traveling to marseilles##7
4. the person traveling to san-francisco is not to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##8
5. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere between the person traveling to paris and the person who's sport is cycling##7
6. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to rome##5
7. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the person traveling to marseilles##8
8. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| City   | paris   | san-francisco | rome | marseilles    |
| Sport         | climbing | rugby   | handball   | cycling |

