.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-6::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, kiwi, lettuce, pineapple
4 different games are played: canasta, whist, backgammon, mah-jongg
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
2. the person playing whist is somewhere to the left of the person eating cauliflower##5
3. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
4. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
5. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere to the left of the person eating kiwi##5
6. the person eating pineapple is not to the left of the person playing whist##8
7. the person eating pineapple is the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food          | pineapple | cauliflower | kiwi  | lettuce |
| Game   | whist   | mah-jongg         | backgammon | canasta |

