.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, dahlia, lily, zinnia
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, cricket, rowing, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is cricket is not to the left of the person who growsdahlia##8
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere between the person who growszinnia and the person who's sport is rowing##7
3. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##5
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is not to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##8
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is not to the left of the person who growsdahlia##8
6. the person who growstulip is on the left or right of the person who growslily##3
7. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
8. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Flower   | dahlia      | lily | tulip | zinnia   |
| Sport      | badminton | rowing | volleyball  | cricket |

