.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-14::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, sprite, tea
There 4 different types of food: pear, artichoke, carrot, orange
1. the person eating orange is not to the left of the person eating artichoke##8
2. the person drinking tea is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating orange is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
4. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking tea and the person eating carrot##2
5. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
6. the person eating pear is between the person eating artichoke and the person eating orange##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |     3      |      4       |
| Beverage   | 7up     | almond-milk | tea        | sprite       |
| Food      | carrot | artichoke  | pear | orange |

