.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, papaya, watermelon, zucchini
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, old-henry, havana, swisher
 1. the swisher-smoker is somewhere to the left of the havana-smoker##5
 2. the person eating zucchini is not to the left of the person eating watermelon##8
 3. the person eating grapefruit is the havana-smoker##1
 4. the havana-smoker is not to the right of the old-henry-smoker##8
 5. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 6. the old-henry-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person eating watermelon##5
 7. the old-henry-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person eating grapefruit is not to the right of the havana-smoker##8
 9. the old-henry-smoker is not to the left of the person eating grapefruit##8
10. the person eating papaya is not to the left of the chaman-smoker##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Food          | papaya    | watermelon | grapefruit | zucchini |
| Cigar   | chaman | swisher  | havana     | old-henry    |

