.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-18::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, jet-ski, snowmobile, van
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, drawing, reading, video-games
1. the person driving the snowmobile is the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is not to the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##8
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person driving the van##1
5. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
6. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the person driving the van##2
7. the person driving the snowmobile is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Transport    | van        | jet-ski | skateboard | snowmobile |
| Hobby   | video-games | reading | drawing   | camping    |

