.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-19::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, fish, rabbit, snake
House: farmhouse, gothic-revival, colonial, art-deco
1. the owner of the snake is not the colonial house##6
2. the colonial house is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
3. the owner of the fish is somewhere between the owner of the rabbit and the owner of the snake##7
4. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the right of the owner of the cat##5
5. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the left of the art-deco house##5
6. the farmhouse house is not to the right of the gothic-revival house##8
7. the owner of the fish is not to the left of the art-deco house##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Pet         | cat  | snake | fish  | rabbit  |
| House   | farmhouse | gothic-revival   | art-deco | colonial |

