.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, frog, hamster, hedgehog
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, traveling, magic-tricks, dancing
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is not the owner of the chinchilla##6
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is not to the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##8
4. the owner of the hamster is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere between the person who's hobby is traveling and the person who's hobby is card-games##7
6. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the person who's hobby is dancing and the owner of the hamster##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet         | frog    | hedgehog | chinchilla | hamster |
| Hobby   | traveling | dancing      | magic-tricks     | card-games     |

 